tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE quantum_experiment_data (
    experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_date DATE,
    qubit_id INT,
    measurement_data FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_measurements (
    measurement_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_id UUID NOT NULL,
    device_id UUID NOT NULL,
    measurement_result FLOAT NOT NULL,
    measurement_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE experiment_data (
  experiment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  quantum_measurement_result VARCHAR(255),
  experiment_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_devices (
  device_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  device_name VARCHAR(50),
  manufacturer VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE experiment_results (
  result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_id INT,
  measurement_data JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE researchers (
  researcher_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  researcher_name VARCHAR(50),
  researcher_email VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE experimental_data (
  experiment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_name TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  qubit_id INT,
  measurement_result FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_devices (
  device_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  device_name TEXT,
  device_type TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE measurements (
  measurement_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  experiment_id UUID,
  qubit_id INT,
  measurement_data JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_gates (
  gate_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  gate_name TEXT,
  gate_matrix JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE qubit_properties (
  qubit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  coherence_time INTERVAL,
  error_rate FLOAT
)
